Rumu,

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:04.760
where are you taking me?

00:04:16.120 --> 00:04:16.880
Rumu,

00:04:17.360 --> 00:04:18.320
this place is…

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:19.240
Quan Rumu!

00:04:19.560 --> 00:04:20.820
You've got some nerve!

00:04:21.079 --> 00:04:22.610
How dare you bring him here?

00:04:26.840 --> 00:04:27.400
Weiyun,

00:04:27.960 --> 00:04:29.290
I've brought him to you.

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:32.140
Do whatever you want with him.

00:04:39.600 --> 00:04:40.520
Miss Long,

00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:45.240
back then, I was possessed
by the Black Fox.

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:48.800
That's why I did those terrible things
to your mother.

00:04:53.600 --> 00:04:55.320
Possessed by the Black Fox?

00:04:55.710 --> 00:04:57.710
You think that excuses everything?

00:05:04.120 --> 00:05:05.040
Miss Long,

00:05:05.880 --> 00:05:06.680
even if

00:05:07.880 --> 00:05:09.840
you cut me

00:05:10.360 --> 00:05:12.120
into 1,000 pieces today,

00:05:13.600 --> 00:05:14.960
I'd have no complaint.

00:05:16.040 --> 00:05:17.880
I just want you to know—

00:05:22.120 --> 00:05:24.560
I truly loved your mother.

00:05:25.280 --> 00:05:26.920
Every time I think of her,

00:05:27.720 --> 00:05:29.560
I'm filled with regret.

00:05:30.640 --> 00:05:32.840
I'm a wreck now,

00:05:34.159 --> 00:05:36.040
and I've long wished to die.

00:05:41.480 --> 00:05:43.159
If I can die by your hand,

00:05:44.360 --> 00:05:45.840
that will be my release.

00:05:59.880 --> 00:06:00.720
Quan Rumu,

00:06:01.680 --> 00:06:03.010
before I change my mind,

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.160
take your father and go home.

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:05.920
Weiyun.

00:06:07.560 --> 00:06:07.840
Weiyun…

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:08.520
Quan Rumu!

00:06:09.840 --> 00:06:12.040
I thought I made myself clear last time.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:14.000
Today is my birthday.

00:06:17.160 --> 00:06:18.120
Do you remember

00:06:18.640 --> 00:06:19.600
our agreement?

00:06:25.640 --> 00:06:26.400
Master.

00:06:29.080 --> 00:06:29.880
Master?

00:06:39.600 --> 00:06:42.400
I've returned
to Sandstorm Town to get something.

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:23.080
Lantern Wang,

00:07:23.440 --> 00:07:24.720
I have an urgent matter.

00:07:24.720 --> 00:07:26.780
Could you help me write a letter home?

00:07:26.960 --> 00:07:27.620
No problem.

00:07:28.320 --> 00:07:29.000
Thank you.

00:07:35.000 --> 00:07:36.530
I'm not sure how to write it.

00:07:36.840 --> 00:07:37.640
I just want

00:07:37.920 --> 00:07:39.720
to send my elder brother a letter

00:07:40.120 --> 00:07:40.950
to tell him

00:07:41.159 --> 00:07:42.600
I'm doing fine here,

00:07:43.159 --> 00:07:44.560
so he won't worry.

00:07:53.840 --> 00:07:54.440
Hey,

00:07:54.600 --> 00:07:55.200
