00:08:22.400 --> 00:08:23.800
make all these yourself?

00:08:24.080 --> 00:08:24.800
That's right.

00:08:24.800 --> 00:08:26.130
I made every one of them.

00:08:26.360 --> 00:08:27.320
I know a bit of fire magic,

00:08:27.320 --> 00:08:28.520
