won't go out in the wind.

00:08:28.520 --> 00:08:29.720
They sell quite well.

00:08:29.880 --> 00:08:30.640
If you'd like one,

00:08:30.640 --> 00:08:32.039
I'll give you a discount.

00:08:36.159 --> 00:08:38.360
I heard you came from the Yiqi Alliance.

00:08:39.880 --> 00:08:41.270
Do you know about the Soldier?

00:08:41.270 --> 00:08:42.200
Who doesn't?

00:08:42.640 --> 00:08:43.960
He consorted with demons.
That's strictly forbidden.

00:08:43.960 --> 00:08:44.760
Though Chief is his father,

00:08:44.760 --> 00:08:45.710
